### 2. Constrained BRSKI and Join Proxy
* **Speaker:** Esko Dijk
* **Slides:** [01 cBRSKI and Join Proxy](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-anima-cbrski-and-join-proxy-00)
* **Associated Drafts:** `draft-ietf-anima-constrained-voucher`, `draft-ietf-anima-constrained-join-proxy`

* **Updates on Constrained Voucher:**
