* **Updates on Constrained Join Proxy:**
  * Aligned terminology with updated onboarding specs.
  * Provided stricter guidance on mode selection (stateless vs. stateful).
  * Refined the definition of the `JPY` protocol scheme and shortened the default multicast discovery message sizes in cooperation with the CoRE Working Group.

